<subSubSection id="C34C655AFFB5534525BFF5685CDEB016" pageId="4" pageNumber="435" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="8BE936D1FFB5534525BFF5685CDEB016" blockId="4.[127,1333,2413,3000]" pageId="4" pageNumber="435">
<emphasis id="B922EAC3FFB5534525BFF5685EDDB181" bold="true" box="[129,483,2767,2800]" pageId="4" pageNumber="435">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Near Threatened on The IUCN Red List. Shipton’s Mountain Cavy has a small and fragmented distribution. Overgrazing in the region is degrading habitat quality. Its distribution overlaps Los Cardones National Park, where it probably receives some protection from disturbance.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
